T*
(his chosen men lay about in the hall, but the workmen had already gone each about his business, the)Tj
T*
(time being the hay-making season. Now when the maiden came in she took up the wood, saying:)Tj
T*
("Sooth, indeed, are most of the old saws; ’so one grows craven as one grows old;’ that honour mostly)Tj
T*
